name: Pleun Herder
summary: Science and Business Management student at the University of Utrecht specializing in biomedical research and business. Passionate about making a positive impact in the healthcare industry through a combination of scientific knowledge and business expertise. Currently conducting a major research project at Antonius Ziekenhuis Nieuwegein for the Pancreatitis Werkgroep Nederland, focusing on genetic profiles in severe acute pancreatitis. Seeking opportunities to contribute to advancements in biomedical research and explore the intersection of science and business in the clinical research field. Let's connect and discuss our shared interests and potential collaborations.
